{
  "id": "27644",
  "key": "DEV-5840",
  "summary": "Add Awards in Sources Panel",
  "description": "We want the AI to have automatic access to high-level past performance insights (dashboard summary metrics and table-level overview) when Past Performance is toggled on, but detailed contract information only when specific contracts are selected. \n\nWhen a user has past performance turned on the ai should be able to answer questions like: \n\n* How many total contracts do we have?\n* How many active contracts do we have?\n* What is the total value of all our contracts?\n* How many SLED contracts do we total? How many do we have active? \n\n!image-20250812-010110.png|width=1422,height=731,alt=\"image-20250812-010110.png\"!",
  "status": {
    "name": "To Do",
    "category": "To Do",
    "color": "blue-gray"
  },
  "priority": {
    "name": "High"
  },
  "assignee": {
