    "id": "27644",
    "key": "DEV-5840",
    "summary": "Add Awards in Sources Panel",
    "url": "https://procurementsciences.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/27644",
    "description": "We would like to add awards to the sources panel. Instead of trying to use the existing past performance nodes, we want to add a separate node called \"awards\".\n\nWhen you expand the config for the awards node, it should show the titles of all the awards that have been imported in the new awards library.\n\nh3. Implementation Plan\n\n* Add a new awards node to the sources panel\n* When expanded, the awards node config should display titles of all imported awards from the new awards library\n* Customers will manually migrate their past performances from the old past performances library to the new awards library\n* Eventually, the old past performances library will be removed\n\nh3. Useful Links\n\n* [Loom video describing the feature|https://www.loom.com/share/56204ab9efb1438fb69a31dec4532ea7?sid=45b119fb-1821-4585-9311-b8e1a6e354e0]\n\nh3. Migration Strategy\n\nCustomers will need to manually migrate their existing past performances from the old library to the new awards library. This is a temporary solution until the old past performances library is deprecated.",
